
#### DESCRIPTION ####

	UYLE (Ultralytics Yolo Label Editor) allow to graphically do mass modification of YOLO's output of label files.



#### USER MANUAL ####


	- PATHS -

		before starting the program, update the differents if necessary in paths.txt : 
		- line 1 : image_folder_paths
		- line 2 : label_folder_paths
		- line 3 :font_file
		- line 4 :model_file


	- CONTROLS -

	left panel :
		scroll to scroll
		click to click
		


	edit area :
		scroll to zoom
		right click to move te picture 
		left click to move label handles
		keep press left click to drag label
		"a" key to add a label
		"d" or "BACKSPACE" key to delete the currently hovered label
		num keys to change the currently hovered label class ID (from 0 to 2 currently)



	label modifications are automatically saved when switching images or closing application
